                    =====================
                       Maildir::Reader
                    =====================

Maildir::Reader allows you to easily read the contents of a Maildir folder.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires no other modules and libraries.

